_json.description: These easy Chickpea Crackers are one of my favorite uses for dukkah spice. They're perfectly crispy, crunchy, and totally addictive. And you won't believe how easy they are to make. These homemade crackers make a great healthy snack all on their own, or enjoy dipping them in your favorite hummus. And they're 100% vegan, vegetarian, and gluten free too! #healthysnack #vegan #glutenfree #dukkah
